This project is a clean-room reimplementation. It was written from scratch in
TypeScript and Go without reference to the source code of the projects listed
below; only their public documentation, README files, and published behavioral
contracts were consulted.

Design inspiration — no code derived:

  - masterix21/laravel-licensing
    https://github.com/masterix21/laravel-licensing
    (PHP, Laravel-specific)

  - masterix21/laravel-licensing-client
    https://github.com/masterix21/laravel-licensing-client
    (PHP, Laravel-specific)

  - masterix21/laravel-licensing-filament-manager
    (PHP, Filament-specific admin UI)

The token format used here ("LIC1") is unique to this project and is NOT
wire-compatible with the `laravel-licensing` token format. A future `LIC2`
revision MAY adopt a PASETO-compatible envelope; the version prefix is
reserved for exactly this kind of forward compatibility.

The cryptographic primitives (Ed25519 via RFC 8032, RSASSA-PSS via RFC 8017,
HMAC-SHA-256 via RFC 2104) are implemented via each language's standard
library. Canonical JSON serialization follows the rules normatively specified
in `fixtures/README.md`.

